---
title: Sarh — Citizen user flow (with NFT licence)
---
flowchart TD
    A([Landing page]) --> B[Sign in / Register]
    B --> C{Has account?}
    C -- No --> C1[Visit ID-Issuer station<br/>to be enrolled] --> END1([End])
    C -- Yes --> D[/Dashboard/]
    D --> E[My Properties]
    D --> F[My Digital ID]
    D --> G[My Wallet<br/>NFT licences]
    D --> H[Profile]

    E --> E1{Properties?}
    E1 -- None --> E2[Register new property]
    E1 -- Has --> E3[Property list]
    E3 --> E4[View detail / status]

    E2 --> E5[Step 1: type + region + address]
    E5 --> E6[Step 2: parcel/plan numbers]
    E6 --> E7[Step 3: pin polygon on map]
    E7 --> E8[Step 4: upload documents]
    E8 --> E9[Submit]
    E9 --> E10{Server validation}
    E10 -- ok --> E11[(status=pending)]
    E10 -- area mismatch --> E5
    E11 --> E12[Wait for officer review]
    E12 --> E13{Officer decision}
    E13 -- needs clarification --> E15[Add docs / reply]
    E15 --> E12
    E13 -- rejected --> E16[See reason]
    E13 -- recommend approval --> E17[Wait for manager approval]
    E17 --> E18{Manager decision}
    E18 -- rejected --> E16
    E18 -- approved --> E19[Receive deed PDF<br/>+ SSI VC<br/>+ NFT licence minted on-chain]

    G --> G1[List of NFT licences]
    G1 --> G2[View token id, contract,<br/>tx hash, current owner]
    G1 --> G3[Initiate transfer<br/>sale / inheritance]

    F --> F1[See current card]
    F1 --> F2{Expiring < 90d?}
    F2 -- yes --> F3[Visit ID-Issuer station]
    F2 -- no --> F4([Done])
